    "| **737–801** | `M._format_task_tool(output, input, metadata, tool_output, duration_text)` — the full task-tool renderer. Key internal steps: |",
    "| **742–752** | Extracts `input.description` and `input.subagent_type`, formats the action header line using `icons.get('task') .. ' task'`. |",
    "| **754–790** | Conditionally (when `config.ui.output.tools.show_output` is true) renders the `metadata.summary` list (each sub-tool with a status icon) and the cleaned `tool_output` text (stripping `<task_metadata>…</task_metadata>` tags). |",
    "| **793–800** | Attaches a `select_child_session` contextual action (`[S]elect Child Session`) covering the rendered task block. |",
